# sopel-norris

Chuck Norris joke plugin for Sopel IRC bots.

## Installing

Releases are hosted on PyPI, so after installing Sopel, all you need is `pip`:

```shell
$ pip install sopel-norris
```

## Changelog

### 0.2.0

Updated for Sopel 8 + modern Python packaging. Now requires Sopel 7.1+ running
on Python 3.8 or higher.


### 0.1.0

First release of `sopel-norris`.
